Sentencas: Nano-sized and spherical shaped LaSrMn oxide particle was synthesized by thermal treatment at 900 degrees C for 3 h after hydrothermally treatment at 200 degrees C for 8 h, and characterized to be applied as a cathode material in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Characteristics of nano-sized perovskite structured LaSrMn derived from hydrothermally synthesized amorphous LaSrMn oxide powder

Sentencas: A spherical LSM nano-particle with sizes ranging from 100 to 120 nm was shown in SEM image and particle size distribution.
Titulo: Characteristics of nano-sized perovskite structured LaSrMn derived from hydrothermally synthesized amorphous LaSrMn oxide powder

Sentencas: The pellets of five types composed of x-wt% LSM synthesized and commercial y-wt% YSZ were manufactured and pre-sintered.
Titulo: Characteristics of nano-sized perovskite structured LaSrMn derived from hydrothermally synthesized amorphous LaSrMn oxide powder

Sentencas: Their ionic conductivities were enhanced responding to LSM concentrations, and it was the highest in 8LSM:2YSZ showing 74.0 S cm(-1).
